<div class=3D"section" id=3D"lobby-info-packet">
<h3>Lobby Info Packet<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://f1-2020-teleme=
try.readthedocs.io/en/stable/telemetry-specification.html#lobby-info-packet=
" title=3D"Permalink to this headline">=C2=B6</a></h3>
<p>This packet details the players currently in a multiplayer lobby.
It details each player=E2=80=99s selected car, any AI involved in the game =
and also the ready status of each of the participants.</p>
<div class=3D"line-block">
<div class=3D"line">Frequency: Two every second when in the lobby</div>
<div class=3D"line">Size: 1169 bytes</div>
<div class=3D"line">Version: 1</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"highlight-c notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre><span>=
</span><span class=3D"k">struct</span> <span class=3D"nc">LobbyInfoData</sp=
an>
<span class=3D"p">{</span>
    <span class=3D"kt">uint8_t</span>   <span class=3D"n">m_aiControlled</s=
pan><span class=3D"p">;</span> <span class=3D"c1">// Whether the vehicle is=
 AI (1) or Human (0) controlled</span>
    <span class=3D"kt">uint8_t</span>   <span class=3D"n">m_teamId</span><s=
pan class=3D"p">;</span>       <span class=3D"c1">// Team id - see appendix=
 (255 if no team currently selected)</span>
    <span class=3D"kt">uint8_t</span>   <span class=3D"n">m_nationality</sp=
an><span class=3D"p">;</span>  <span class=3D"c1">// Nationality of the dri=
ver</span>
    <span class=3D"kt">char</span>      <span class=3D"n">m_name</span><spa=
n class=3D"p">[</span><span class=3D"mi">48</span><span class=3D"p">];</spa=
n>     <span class=3D"c1">// Name of participant in UTF-8 format =E2=80=93 =
null terminated</span>
                              <span class=3D"c1">// Will be truncated with =
... (U+2026) if too long</span>
    <span class=3D"kt">uint8_t</span>   <span class=3D"n">m_readyStatus</sp=
an><span class=3D"p">;</span>  <span class=3D"c1">// 0 =3D not ready, 1 =3D=
 ready, 2 =3D spectating</span>
<span class=3D"p">};</span>

